1942;;Right to the Heart;;American;;Eugene Forde;;Brenda Joyce, Stanley Clements;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Right_to_the_Heart;;John T. Bromley III is a young man from high society who is physically humiliated by a prizefighter before his socialite sweetheart, Jenny Killian. He goes to a training camp to redeem his self-respect and ensure his success in a return engagement with the fighter.